1
00:00:05,570 --> 00:00:06,600
<font color="yellow">(Episode 26)</font>

2
00:00:15,840 --> 00:00:18,440
<font color="yellow">Do you want me to drop your murder charges...</font>

3
00:00:18,440 --> 00:00:21,600
<font color="yellow">and give you some share of the blueprint?</font>

4
00:00:22,570 --> 00:00:25,530
<font color="yellow">- Yes.
- I have a condition, too.</font>

5
00:00:25,530 --> 00:00:26,540
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

6
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:29,640
<font color="yellow">Why don't you come work for me?</font>

7
00:00:35,440 --> 00:00:36,440
<font color="yellow">Are you asking me...</font>

8
00:00:37,270 --> 00:00:39,680
<font color="yellow">to become a member of Huaping?</font>

9
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:41,170
<font color="yellow">Not just a member.</font>

10
00:00:42,170 --> 00:00:44,440
<font color="yellow">I'm asking you to be my right-hand man.</font>

11
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:47,740
<font color="yellow">You'll be the second-in-command.</font>

12
00:01:02,070 --> 00:01:03,100
<font color="yellow">That was...</font>

13
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:04,840
<font color="yellow">not part of my plan.</font>

14
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:07,140
<font color="yellow">It wasn't in mine either.</font>

15
00:01:07,140 --> 00:01:11,240
<font color="yellow">I would never make this offer to anyone else from now on.</font>

16
00:01:18,870 --> 00:01:21,000
<font color="yellow">Answer me, Gi Tan.</font>

17
00:01:22,540 --> 00:01:24,700
<font color="yellow">Will you take my offer?</font>

18
00:02:08,470 --> 00:02:10,170
<font color="yellow">- Gi Tan!
- Gi Tan!</font>

19
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,090
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan!</font>

20
00:02:16,090 --> 00:02:18,210
<font color="yellow">- You have to go, Boss.
- Hurry up.</font>

21
00:02:20,570 --> 00:02:22,100
<font color="yellow">- Don't shoot.
- Move.</font>

22
00:02:23,270 --> 00:02:25,270
<font color="yellow">Don't shoot. You shot Gi Tan.</font>

23
00:02:25,270 --> 00:02:26,270
<font color="yellow">Move away!</font>

24
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:36,840
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan.</font>

25
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,040
<font color="yellow">Where did it come from?</font>

26
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,160
<font color="yellow">Across the river, Boss.</font>

27
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,370
<font color="yellow">Start the car.</font>

28
00:02:41,970 --> 00:02:43,600
<font color="yellow">Hold on, Gi Tan.</font>

29
00:02:48,170 --> 00:02:49,170
<font color="yellow">Get him in the car.</font>

30
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:03,040
<font color="yellow">Stop it, Cha Woo. We failed.</font>

31
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,800
<font color="yellow">No, it's not over yet.</font>

32
00:03:15,100 --> 00:03:17,570
<font color="yellow">- What is that?
- I installed a bomb...</font>

33
00:03:17,570 --> 00:03:20,000
<font color="yellow">just in case we fail.</font>

34
00:03:21,970 --> 00:03:23,500
<font color="yellow">Our plan will end perfectly...</font>

35
00:03:24,170 --> 00:03:26,640
<font color="yellow">if those four people die.</font>

36
00:03:27,270 --> 00:03:28,270
<font color="yellow">No, Cha Woo.</font>

37
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:29,700
<font color="yellow">Don't press it.</font>

38
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:33,530
<font color="yellow">Why? Are you sad to see Gi Tan die?</font>

39
00:03:33,530 --> 00:03:34,770
<font color="yellow">Don't do it!</font>

40
00:03:35,900 --> 00:03:36,940
<font color="yellow">Watch me.</font>

41
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:40,270
<font color="yellow">This bomb will be the firework that blesses...</font>

42
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:41,700
<font color="yellow">our brand new beginning.</font>

43
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:46,940
<font color="yellow">No!</font>

44
00:03:51,170 --> 00:03:52,170
<font color="yellow">Don't get in the way.</font>

45
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:54,940
<font color="yellow">This is for the both of us.</font>

46
00:04:02,170 --> 00:04:03,170
<font color="yellow">Hurry up.</font>

47
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,710
<font color="yellow">Yes, what?</font>

48
00:04:07,710 --> 00:04:10,330
<font color="yellow">Please get out. There's a bomb in there.</font>

49
00:04:10,330 --> 00:04:11,340
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

50
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,440
<font color="yellow">Cha Woo has...</font>

51
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:23,870
<font color="yellow">Drop it.</font>

52
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:25,470
<font color="yellow">You started this.</font>

53
00:04:26,470 --> 00:04:28,870
<font color="yellow">Are you trying to back out...</font>

54
00:04:29,770 --> 00:04:30,950
<font color="yellow">because of Gi Tan?</font>

55
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:32,370
<font color="yellow">Drop it, Cha Woo.</font>

56
00:04:35,670 --> 00:04:36,670
<font color="yellow">Shoot me if you can.</font>

57
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:39,940
<font color="yellow">I know that you can't.</font>

58
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:42,070
<font color="yellow">Please.</font>

59
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:44,100
<font color="yellow">Our lives will change...</font>

60
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:47,510
<font color="yellow">with this button.</font>

61
00:05:35,470 --> 00:05:36,470
<font color="yellow">I killed...</font>

62
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:38,240
<font color="yellow">Cha Woo.</font>

63
00:05:59,570 --> 00:06:00,570
<font color="yellow">Cha Woo...</font>

64
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,840
<font color="yellow">It's me, Mr Jang.</font>

65
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:11,400
<font color="yellow">There's someone you need to save right now.</font>

66
00:06:11,870 --> 00:06:13,300
<font color="yellow">It's a gunshot wound, so he can't go to the hospital.</font>

67
00:06:13,670 --> 00:06:16,370
<font color="yellow">There's an operating room near Cheongpyeong. Meet us there now.</font>

68
00:06:19,970 --> 00:06:21,700
<font color="yellow">- Leo.
- Yes, Boss.</font>

69
00:06:21,700 --> 00:06:25,040
<font color="yellow">Call the boys to clean up the area.</font>

70
00:06:26,300 --> 00:06:28,040
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan and Sung Ae...</font>

71
00:06:28,740 --> 00:06:31,240
<font color="yellow">both died today from the explosion.</font>

72
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:35,000
<font color="yellow">Hyeong Gu and Il Jae are on the same side.</font>

73
00:06:35,670 --> 00:06:36,900
<font color="yellow">So if we want to fake our deaths,</font>

74
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:38,600
<font color="yellow">we have to fool Hyeong Gu first.</font>

75
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,630
<font color="yellow">I'll get rid of him.</font>

76
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:42,370
<font color="yellow">He's an executive of the NIS.</font>

77
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:46,440
<font color="yellow">We don't want to get in trouble. Leak fake rumours instead.</font>

78
00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:47,470
<font color="yellow">Yes, Boss.</font>

79
00:07:00,340 --> 00:07:01,640
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan!</font>

80
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:03,070
<font color="yellow">Wake up!</font>

81
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,600
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan, wake up!</font>

82
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:10,000
<font color="yellow">- Gi Tan. Wake up...
- Wake up!</font>

83
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:13,770
<font color="yellow">Please. You can't die.</font>

84
00:07:14,170 --> 00:07:15,940
<font color="yellow">You promised you'd come back.</font>

85
00:07:17,540 --> 00:07:19,940
<font color="yellow">Jeong Eun. Jeong Eun.</font>

86
00:07:19,940 --> 00:07:21,970
<font color="yellow">Please, Guk Cheol.</font>

87
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:24,770
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan. Gi Tan.</font>

88
00:07:29,370 --> 00:07:31,840
<font color="yellow">Don't go. Don't.</font>

89
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:34,500
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Soo Yeon. I have to go.</font>

90
00:07:34,900 --> 00:07:36,670
<font color="yellow">You can't. Don't go!</font>

91
00:07:36,670 --> 00:07:40,300
<font color="yellow">Don't go, Gi Tan. Please don't leave me...</font>

92
00:07:41,340 --> 00:07:42,370
<font color="yellow">Please...</font>

93
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:45,340
<font color="yellow">Don't go, Gi Tan.</font>

94
00:07:49,770 --> 00:07:50,840
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan.</font>

95
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:53,900
<font color="yellow">Is everything all right?</font>

96
00:08:20,300 --> 00:08:22,940
<font color="yellow">- Cha Woo betrayed me?
- Yes.</font>

97
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:26,400
<font color="yellow">I saw him take a sniper rifle, so I tailed him.</font>

98
00:08:26,970 --> 00:08:28,770
<font color="yellow">Why did he betray me?</font>

99
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:33,540
<font color="yellow">I think he was eyeing the blueprint Gi Tan has.</font>

100
00:08:38,700 --> 00:08:40,400
<font color="yellow">Where's Gi Tan?</font>

101
00:08:46,170 --> 00:08:47,390
<font color="yellow">How did it go?</font>

102
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:49,170
<font color="yellow">I did all I could with the emergency treatment,</font>

103
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:51,300
<font color="yellow">but I'm concerned about the bullet in his head.</font>

104
00:08:53,270 --> 00:08:54,610
<font color="yellow">What will happen to him?</font>

105
00:08:55,340 --> 00:08:57,000
<font color="yellow">It's a miracle he's still alive.</font>

106
00:08:57,840 --> 00:09:00,270
<font color="yellow">It's stuck in a difficult area. If we end up making a mistake...</font>

107
00:09:01,340 --> 00:09:03,440
<font color="yellow">- during surgery...
- So?</font>

108
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,900
<font color="yellow">What will happen to him.</font>

109
00:09:05,900 --> 00:09:07,340
<font color="yellow">It's hard to say that...</font>

110
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,900
<font color="yellow">he'll make it out alive at this stage.</font>

111
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,740
<font color="yellow">He took the hit for me.</font>

112
00:09:18,070 --> 00:09:19,970
<font color="yellow">His life is the same as mine.</font>

113
00:09:20,570 --> 00:09:23,170
<font color="yellow">You have to save him no matter what. No matter what!</font>

114
00:09:23,610 --> 00:09:27,340
<font color="yellow">I did my best. Let's wait and see.</font>

115
00:09:38,740 --> 00:09:40,840
<font color="yellow">You love kimchijjigae.</font>

116
00:09:42,110 --> 00:09:43,110
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

117
00:09:44,140 --> 00:09:45,840
<font color="yellow">You should eat more.</font>

118
00:09:46,370 --> 00:09:48,270
<font color="yellow">It'll give you more energy.</font>

119
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,000
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

120
00:09:53,270 --> 00:09:55,290
<font color="yellow">Yesterday, near Yangju Bridge,</font>

121
00:09:55,290 --> 00:09:58,720
<font color="yellow">a car exploded and fell into the river.</font>

122
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:02,240
<font color="yellow">The police are investigating nearby security cameras and witnesses,</font>

123
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:06,000
<font color="yellow">and they believe that the people inside the car were...</font>

124
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:09,570
<font color="yellow">the escaped prisoner Kang and his accomplice Yoo.</font>

125
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:13,670
<font color="yellow">- Isn't that Gi Tan?
- In the damaged car,</font>

126
00:10:13,670 --> 00:10:15,570
<font color="yellow">police found their personal belongings.</font>

127
00:10:16,110 --> 00:10:18,200
<font color="yellow">The police are assuming that it was a suicide...</font>

128
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:21,110
<font color="yellow">and have started a search to find the bodies.</font>

129
00:10:24,110 --> 00:10:26,450
<font color="yellow">Are you sure Gi Tan's dead?</font>

130
00:10:26,450 --> 00:10:27,840
<font color="yellow">Yes, I'm sure.</font>

131
00:10:30,900 --> 00:10:34,340
<font color="yellow">You shouldn't believe anything until they find his body.</font>

132
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:39,140
<font color="yellow">Huaping is good at cleaning up after themselves.</font>

133
00:10:39,770 --> 00:10:41,240
<font color="yellow">It'll be impossible to find their bodies.</font>

134
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:48,400
<font color="yellow">Coma? Gi Tan is in a coma?</font>

135
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:50,110
<font color="yellow">His brain is alive,</font>

136
00:10:50,670 --> 00:10:52,200
<font color="yellow">but he's unconscious.</font>

137
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,580
<font color="yellow">When will he wake up?</font>

138
00:10:55,580 --> 00:10:58,270
<font color="yellow">It could be a month or a year.</font>

139
00:10:58,270 --> 00:10:59,740
<font color="yellow">He may never wake up at all.</font>

140
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:20,240
<font color="yellow">I'll call you back later.</font>

141
00:11:20,970 --> 00:11:23,470
<font color="yellow">Did Gi Tan really die?</font>

142
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,940
<font color="yellow">I saw the corpse myself.</font>

143
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,840
<font color="yellow">I have to see it myself to believe it.</font>

144
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:33,500
<font color="yellow">If you want everyone to know that you're behind this, go ahead.</font>

145
00:11:33,870 --> 00:11:34,870
<font color="yellow">I'll call back.</font>

146
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:44,170
<font color="yellow">I won't be having nightmares about Guk Cheol any more.</font>

147
00:12:09,870 --> 00:12:10,870
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Gi Tan.</font>

148
00:12:13,900 --> 00:12:14,940
<font color="yellow">My greed...</font>

149
00:12:16,470 --> 00:12:17,840
<font color="yellow">did this to you.</font>

150
00:12:20,970 --> 00:12:22,200
<font color="yellow">Forgive me.</font>

151
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:50,940
<font color="yellow">She's up to something for sure.</font>

152
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:15,700
<font color="yellow">Is Soo Yeon still looking for Gi Tan?</font>

153
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:18,540
<font color="yellow">Please look out for him.</font>

154
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,640
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

155
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:28,240
<font color="yellow">She's going around police stations and hospitals.</font>

156
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,620
<font color="yellow">Why hospitals?</font>

157
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:32,790
<font color="yellow">She's trying to see if any of the unidentified patients...</font>

158
00:13:32,790 --> 00:13:34,540
<font color="yellow">might be him.</font>

159
00:13:41,700 --> 00:13:47,100
<font color="yellow">(Hangang Hospital)</font>

160
00:13:57,800 --> 00:14:00,640
<font color="yellow">Why do you look so shabby? Did you even eat?</font>

161
00:14:00,970 --> 00:14:02,070
<font color="yellow">I told you to leave me alone.</font>

162
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,470
<font color="yellow">How long are you going to be like this?</font>

163
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:08,140
<font color="yellow">I don't have the energy to talk to you.</font>

164
00:14:08,500 --> 00:14:09,670
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan is dead!</font>

165
00:14:12,870 --> 00:14:14,040
<font color="yellow">He's not dead.</font>

166
00:14:18,500 --> 00:14:20,100
<font color="yellow">Wake up, Soo Yeon!</font>

167
00:14:20,940 --> 00:14:23,200
<font color="yellow">Let me go. Let me go!</font>

168
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:25,160
<font color="yellow">A dead man won't come back even if you do this.</font>

169
00:14:25,160 --> 00:14:26,600
<font color="yellow">He's alive.</font>

170
00:14:27,070 --> 00:14:30,270
<font color="yellow">He's alive. I'm sure of it. He has to be alive!</font>

171
00:14:31,900 --> 00:14:33,000
<font color="yellow">Just accept it.</font>

172
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,770
<font color="yellow">You already know that he's dead.</font>

173
00:15:06,570 --> 00:15:09,370
<font color="yellow">Find out what Gwang Woo is up to these days.</font>

174
00:15:10,540 --> 00:15:11,570
<font color="yellow">Sorry?</font>

175
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,270
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

176
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:23,370
<font color="yellow">Are you looking down at me because I'm a regular worker?</font>

177
00:15:23,370 --> 00:15:24,440
<font color="yellow">- No, Sir!
- No, Sir!</font>

178
00:15:28,770 --> 00:15:29,870
<font color="yellow">Chief Oh, stand up.</font>

179
00:15:37,370 --> 00:15:38,400
<font color="yellow">Chief Oh.</font>

180
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,200
<font color="yellow">Do you think...</font>

181
00:15:40,770 --> 00:15:42,540
<font color="yellow">I'm a joke?</font>

182
00:15:43,540 --> 00:15:44,570
<font color="yellow">Not at all.</font>

183
00:15:44,570 --> 00:15:46,370
<font color="yellow">Then why are you telling me to work?</font>

184
00:15:47,340 --> 00:15:50,640
<font color="yellow">How dare you order me around?</font>

185
00:15:53,100 --> 00:15:54,170
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

186
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:00,300
<font color="yellow">Head down.</font>

187
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:10,100
<font color="yellow">Hey, hey, hey! Raise your hands up higher!</font>

188
00:16:18,100 --> 00:16:19,270
<font color="yellow">How's Gwang Woo doing?</font>

189
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:21,260
<font color="yellow">Nothing has changed.</font>

190
00:16:21,260 --> 00:16:22,300
<font color="yellow">Can you...</font>

191
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:25,070
<font color="yellow">make him into a worthy man?</font>

192
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:28,280
<font color="yellow">How could I do something even you couldn't do?</font>

193
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:29,740
<font color="yellow">Could you do it...</font>

194
00:16:30,670 --> 00:16:32,540
<font color="yellow">if I gave you all of my authorities?</font>

195
00:16:32,540 --> 00:16:34,470
<font color="yellow">Authorities?</font>

196
00:16:34,470 --> 00:16:35,640
<font color="yellow">All authorities to him...</font>

197
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:38,640
<font color="yellow">as his father and Chairman.</font>

198
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:44,100
<font color="yellow">Even kings can't change their children.</font>

199
00:16:45,270 --> 00:16:46,900
<font color="yellow">If you give up on him,</font>

200
00:16:47,940 --> 00:16:50,140
<font color="yellow">I'll have to give up on him, too.</font>

201
00:16:51,540 --> 00:16:52,900
<font color="yellow">I hope you can...</font>

202
00:16:53,700 --> 00:16:54,740
<font color="yellow">accept this offer...</font>

203
00:16:55,900 --> 00:16:57,640
<font color="yellow">for his sake.</font>

204
00:17:00,470 --> 00:17:01,500
<font color="yellow">Please make sure...</font>

205
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:04,110
<font color="yellow">nothing will happen to me, Chairman.</font>

206
00:17:04,110 --> 00:17:06,370
<font color="yellow">Nothing will happen to you even if that means...</font>

207
00:17:07,170 --> 00:17:08,640
<font color="yellow">I have to let Gwang Woo go.</font>

208
00:17:09,040 --> 00:17:10,040
<font color="yellow">I understand,</font>

209
00:17:10,570 --> 00:17:11,600
<font color="yellow">Chairman.</font>

210
00:17:22,170 --> 00:17:23,400
<font color="yellow">Hey, Chief Secretary Moon.</font>

211
00:17:26,840 --> 00:17:29,840
<font color="yellow">Did Father say anything about me?</font>

212
00:17:31,100 --> 00:17:35,670
<font color="yellow">Did he say anything about how long I have to be at the storage?</font>

213
00:17:36,140 --> 00:17:37,700
<font color="yellow">Follow me if you want to know.</font>

214
00:17:44,540 --> 00:17:46,740
<font color="yellow">What? Make me into a man?</font>

215
00:17:47,740 --> 00:17:51,330
<font color="yellow">He asked you to make me into a man, right?</font>

216
00:17:51,330 --> 00:17:52,370
