00:33:17,900 --> 00:33:21,900
<font color="yellow">Sir. Did you forget about the order you gave me?</font>

432
00:33:23,300 --> 00:33:24,340
<font color="yellow">Hold on.</font>

433
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:28,640
<font color="yellow">I have a headache.</font>

434
00:33:31,170 --> 00:33:32,200
<font color="yellow">Right.</font>

435
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:34,840
<font color="yellow">I remember it now.</font>

436
00:33:35,540 --> 00:33:36,570
<font color="yellow">I told you...</font>

437
00:33:37,200 --> 00:33:38,970
<font color="yellow">to teach him a lesson.</font>

438
00:33:42,040 --> 00:33:43,300
<font color="yellow">It's time for the EGM.</font>

439
00:33:44,140 --> 00:33:45,300
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

440
00:33:55,670 --> 00:33:57,870
<font color="yellow">Is he all right?</font>

441
00:33:57,870 --> 00:34:00,280
<font color="yellow">It's normal for a human to be forgetful sometimes.</font>

442
00:34:00,280 --> 00:34:03,470
<font color="yellow">I've reported three times already, but he looked so clueless.</font>

443
00:34:03,970 --> 00:34:06,430
<font color="yellow">I have to escort him for now.</font>

444
00:34:06,430 --> 00:34:07,670
<font color="yellow">We'll talk later.</font>

445
00:34:15,970 --> 00:34:17,800
<font color="yellow">How can he forget that...</font>

446
00:34:18,300 --> 00:34:20,210
<font color="yellow">after making me the bad guy?</font>

447
00:34:24,300 --> 00:34:27,900
<font color="yellow">(Dodo Group Extraordinary General Meeting)</font>

448
00:34:27,900 --> 00:34:30,400
<font color="yellow">It's been a while, Chairman Do.</font>

449
00:34:30,800 --> 00:34:32,300
<font color="yellow">Why are you here?</font>

450
00:34:32,300 --> 00:34:35,970
<font color="yellow">An extraordinary general meeting isn't a party.</font>

451
00:34:36,640 --> 00:34:40,240
<font color="yellow">Obviously, I'm not here for the food.</font>

452
00:34:40,240 --> 00:34:41,640
<font color="yellow">That's why I'm asking.</font>

453
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:43,900
<font color="yellow">He came as a shareholder.</font>

454
00:34:47,340 --> 00:34:50,140
<font color="yellow">I gave all my shares to him.</font>

455
00:34:51,540 --> 00:34:52,940
<font color="yellow">Are you teaming up...</font>

456
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:55,300
<font color="yellow">to kick Gun Woo out?</font>

457
00:34:56,640 --> 00:34:58,000
<font color="yellow">There are a lot of eyes on you.</font>

458
00:34:58,000 --> 00:35:00,540
<font color="yellow">Don't you consider saving face more important than your wife?</font>

459
00:35:00,540 --> 00:35:01,570
<font color="yellow">It won't...</font>

460
00:35:02,600 --> 00:35:04,470
<font color="yellow">ever go as you planned.</font>

461
00:35:05,470 --> 00:35:06,540
<font color="yellow">You'll see.</font>

462
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:18,300
<font color="yellow">When is Director Byun coming?</font>

463
00:35:18,300 --> 00:35:20,570
<font color="yellow">He won't be late, don't worry.</font>

464
00:35:20,570 --> 00:35:21,900
<font color="yellow">Let's go inside.</font>

465
00:35:22,870 --> 00:35:23,870
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

466
00:35:39,100 --> 00:35:40,710
<font color="yellow">Il Jae's father-in-law is here.</font>

467
00:35:41,670 --> 00:35:44,500
<font color="yellow">Are you sure he'll make the deal with you?</font>

468
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:50,100
<font color="yellow">According to my intelligence, the two of them...</font>

469
00:35:50,670 --> 00:35:52,270
<font color="yellow">have gone their separate ways.</font>

470
00:35:54,740 --> 00:35:58,680
<font color="yellow">Before we get into the issue of the Vice Chairman's position,</font>

471
00:35:58,680 --> 00:35:59,970
<font color="yellow">the chairman will say a few words.</font>

472
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:04,800
<font color="yellow">- Let me.
- I'm fine. It's okay.</font>

473
00:36:12,070 --> 00:36:13,710
<font color="yellow">I'll keep it short.</font>

474
00:36:14,500 --> 00:36:15,840
<font color="yellow">Vice Chairman Do Gun Woo...</font>

475
00:36:16,500 --> 00:36:18,270
<font color="yellow">has all but signed the contract...</font>

476
00:36:18,770 --> 00:36:20,040
<font color="yellow">to produce...</font>

477
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:22,800
<font color="yellow">the vaccine to the mutant virus.</font>

478
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:25,070
<font color="yellow">What's going on?</font>

479
00:36:25,070 --> 00:36:26,600
<font color="yellow">Is this true?</font>

480
00:36:29,140 --> 00:36:30,840
<font color="yellow">You must know...</font>

481
00:36:31,300 --> 00:36:34,570
<font color="yellow">better than anyone what that means for...</font>

482
00:36:36,370 --> 00:36:39,170
<font color="yellow">the future of our company.</font>

483
00:36:39,170 --> 00:36:40,710
<font color="yellow">Of course, we do.</font>

484
00:36:41,340 --> 00:36:42,950
<font color="yellow">If we sign the contract,</font>

485
00:36:42,950 --> 00:36:46,090
<font color="yellow">then you must promote Vice Chairman Do.</font>

486
00:36:46,090 --> 00:36:49,090
<font color="yellow">When will the contract be signed?</font>

487
00:36:49,090 --> 00:36:52,240
<font color="yellow">The CEO of the company that developed it is here.</font>

488
00:37:15,210 --> 00:37:16,600
<font color="yellow">It's good to see you again.</font>

489
00:37:17,370 --> 00:37:21,270
<font color="yellow">Our shareholders would like to know...</font>

490
00:37:22,240 --> 00:37:24,400
<font color="yellow">whom you decided to sign with.</font>

491
00:37:27,340 --> 00:37:29,800
<font color="yellow">May I tell them myself?</font>

492
00:37:30,710 --> 00:37:31,710
<font color="yellow">You may.</font>

493
00:37:44,300 --> 00:37:46,400
<font color="yellow">I'm Byun Il Jae, the CEO of B World.</font>

494
00:37:47,270 --> 00:37:50,210
<font color="yellow">I decided to enter into a technical partnership...</font>

495
00:37:50,600 --> 00:37:52,210
<font color="yellow">with Dodo Group because...</font>

496
00:37:54,100 --> 00:37:55,970
<font color="yellow">I was greatly moved...</font>

497
00:37:57,640 --> 00:37:59,540
<font color="yellow">by one person's passion.</font>

498
00:38:06,270 --> 00:38:07,300
<font color="yellow">Executive Director Do Gwang Woo.</font>

499
00:38:07,900 --> 00:38:08,970
<font color="yellow">Come and join me.</font>

500
00:38:49,100 --> 00:38:51,740
<font color="yellow">Put the vice chairman's dismissal to a vote.</font>

501
00:38:52,070 --> 00:38:56,210
<font color="yellow">Shouldn't we reinstate Do Gwang Woo as the CEO of Dodo Pharmaceutical?</font>

502
00:38:56,210 --> 00:38:59,680
<font color="yellow">Let's lay an urgent bill and vote right now.</font>

503
00:38:59,680 --> 00:39:01,470
<font color="yellow">Let's just vote.</font>

504
00:39:01,470 --> 00:39:02,500
<font color="yellow">Let's vote.</font>

505
00:39:04,210 --> 00:39:05,770
<font color="yellow">- Father.
- Dad!</font>

506
00:39:07,100 --> 00:39:08,160
<font color="yellow">- Sir.
- Sir.</font>

507
00:39:08,160 --> 00:39:09,710
<font color="yellow">- Father!
- Chairman!</font>

508
00:39:13,900 --> 00:39:15,340
<font color="yellow">- Sir.
- Sir.</font>

509
00:39:15,340 --> 00:39:16,490
<font color="yellow">Take him out.</font>

510
00:39:16,490 --> 00:39:17,670
<font color="yellow">Gently.</font>

511
00:39:39,600 --> 00:39:42,400
<font color="yellow">Mr Do just went into surgery.</font>

512
00:39:44,070 --> 00:39:46,780
<font color="yellow">- Surgery?
- We'll have to wait and see,</font>

513
00:39:46,780 --> 00:39:48,640
<font color="yellow">but the worst is over.</font>

514
00:39:49,500 --> 00:39:50,570
<font color="yellow">Get the car ready.</font>

515
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:52,000
<font color="yellow">Yes, Ma'am.</font>

516
00:40:08,500 --> 00:40:10,040
<font color="yellow">I know quite a few people...</font>

517
00:40:10,400 --> 00:40:13,170
<font color="yellow">who would be devastated if my father collapsed.</font>

518
00:40:14,710 --> 00:40:16,170
<font color="yellow">What are you implying?</font>

519
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:19,000
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

520
00:40:19,340 --> 00:40:21,470
<font color="yellow">Don't put on a show.</font>

521
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:23,790
<font color="yellow">You aren't worried for him.</font>

522
00:40:23,790 --> 00:40:25,640
<font color="yellow">You're worried for your future.</font>

523
00:40:26,300 --> 00:40:28,140
<font color="yellow">Your father's in surgery.</font>

524
00:40:28,500 --> 00:40:29,500
<font color="yellow">Please stop.</font>

525
00:40:30,140 --> 00:40:33,880
<font color="yellow">What did you say in your job interview?</font>

526
00:40:33,880 --> 00:40:36,270
<font color="yellow">You said you wanted to succeed and make your father pay.</font>

527
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:39,240
<font color="yellow">You got your way. You must be pleased.</font>

528
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:44,130
<font color="yellow">Did he really say that?</font>

529
00:40:44,130 --> 00:40:45,740
<font color="yellow">Will you please stop?</font>

530
00:40:52,540 --> 00:40:53,640
<font color="yellow">Why are you here?</font>

531
00:40:55,710 --> 00:40:56,710
<font color="yellow">Send him away.</font>

532
00:40:59,600 --> 00:41:02,000
<font color="yellow">Can I stay until he wakes up?</font>

533
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:03,300
<font color="yellow">Get him out of here.</font>

534
00:41:03,300 --> 00:41:06,080
<font color="yellow">Ma'am, you can't do this.</font>

535
00:41:06,080 --> 00:41:07,340
<font color="yellow">Why not?</font>

536
00:41:07,340 --> 00:41:09,000
<font color="yellow">Do you want to join him?</font>

537
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,700
<font color="yellow">He is Chairman's son.</font>

538
00:41:10,700 --> 00:41:13,040
<font color="yellow">- He should get to see...
- Chief Secretary Moon.</font>

539
00:41:13,500 --> 00:41:15,210
<font color="yellow">Shut your mouth.</font>

540
00:41:16,340 --> 00:41:17,570
<font color="yellow">Get him out of here.</font>

541
00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:30,640
<font color="yellow">Until my husband is fully able,</font>

542
00:41:31,170 --> 00:41:33,270
<font color="yellow">I will make all the important decisions.</font>

543
00:41:33,640 --> 00:41:35,800
<font color="yellow">Do you both understand?</font>

544
00:41:51,100 --> 00:41:53,940
<font color="yellow">There's one thing that those who dislike...</font>

545
00:41:53,940 --> 00:41:55,710
<font color="yellow">and envy you don't know.</font>

546
00:41:57,710 --> 00:42:00,300
<font color="yellow">They don't know how incredibly proud I am of you.</font>

547
00:42:03,240 --> 00:42:05,540
<font color="yellow">Bear with me and hang in there.</font>

548
00:42:06,440 --> 00:42:07,770
<font color="yellow">I will make you...</font>

549
00:42:09,270 --> 00:42:12,000
<font color="yellow">a thousand times greater than you are now.</font>

550
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:15,000
<font color="yellow">No one...</font>

551
00:42:16,170 --> 00:42:18,940
<font color="yellow">will be able to mock my son.</font>

552
00:42:20,600 --> 00:42:22,210
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Father.</font>

553
00:42:29,970 --> 00:42:31,240
<font color="yellow">I'm so sorry.</font>

554
00:42:51,370 --> 00:42:52,370
<font color="yellow">I don't...</font>

555
00:42:53,500 --> 00:42:55,170
<font color="yellow">pity you at all.</font>

556
00:42:56,210 --> 00:42:57,570
<font color="yellow">Why should I?</font>

557
00:42:58,640 --> 00:43:00,000
<font color="yellow">You had everything.</font>

558
00:43:01,970 --> 00:43:03,540
<font color="yellow">You tortured everybody.</font>

559
00:43:09,800 --> 00:43:10,870
<font color="yellow">Don't get it wrong.</font>

560
00:43:12,500 --> 00:43:13,500
<font color="yellow">These tears...</font>

561
00:43:15,400 --> 00:43:17,100
<font color="yellow">are for poor, little me.</font>

562
00:43:20,970 --> 00:43:22,770
<font color="yellow">You hated me all your life,</font>

563
00:43:24,500 --> 00:43:26,670
<font color="yellow">and now, I can hate you back.</font>

564
00:43:28,900 --> 00:43:30,940
<font color="yellow">I'm crying over the past that I lost.</font>

565
00:43:35,600 --> 00:43:36,800
<font color="yellow">Lie here in comfort...</font>

566
00:43:38,300 --> 00:43:40,300
<font color="yellow">and watch what I do next.</font>

567
00:43:43,700 --> 00:43:44,870
<font color="yellow">You used me...</font>

568
00:43:46,400 --> 00:43:48,270
<font color="yellow">to create this world.</font>

569
00:43:49,640 --> 00:43:51,140
<font color="yellow">Now, I'm in control.</font>

570
00:44:10,000 --> 00:44:11,440
<font color="yellow">(Hwang Gwi Ja, Dodo's Interim Chairperson)</font>

571
00:44:17,500 --> 00:44:18,740
<font color="yellow">Chairwoman is here.</font>

572
00:44:32,500 --> 00:44:33,800
<font color="yellow">Take this opportunity...</font>

573
00:44:34,970 --> 00:44:37,670
<font color="yellow">to get rid of all your father's allies.</font>

574
00:44:37,670 --> 00:44:40,670
<font color="yellow">He'll come back to Korea once he recovers.</font>

575
00:44:41,300 --> 00:44:43,500
<font color="yellow">What if he gets furious?</font>

576
00:44:43,500 --> 00:44:45,500
<font color="yellow">He might not come back to work.</font>

577
00:44:46,140 --> 00:44:48,280
<font color="yellow">He's making progress.</font>

578
00:44:48,280 --> 00:44:50,370
<font color="yellow">That's why we have to work fast.</font>

579
00:44:50,370 --> 00:44:51,800
<font color="yellow">So he can't do anything on his return.</font>

580
00:44:52,170 --> 00:44:54,300
<font color="yellow">What about Gun Woo?</font>

581
00:44:55,370 --> 00:44:56,740
<font color="yellow">He lost his title.</font>

582
00:44:57,200 --> 00:44:59,200
<font color="yellow">Deal with him later to avoid scrutiny.</font>

583
00:45:03,170 --> 00:45:05,200
<font color="yellow">Look at all these names.</font>

584
00:45:05,200 --> 00:45:08,140
<font color="yellow">I wonder whom I should start with first.</font>

585
00:45:08,500 --> 00:45:09,500
<font color="yellow">It's so much work.</font>

586
00:45:13,240 --> 00:45:14,240
<font color="yellow">Starting today,</font>

587
00:45:14,700 --> 00:45:18,370
<font color="yellow">we will shuffle personnel and restructure the organisation.</font>

588
00:45:20,770 --> 00:45:21,900
<font color="yellow">CEO Do Gwang Woo...</font>

589
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:24,780
<font color="yellow">will be in charge.</font>

590
00:45:24,780 --> 00:45:25,840
<font color="yellow">Yes, Chairwoman.</font>

591
00:45:26,700 --> 00:45:27,770
<font color="yellow">Before we begin...</font>

592
00:45:29,500 --> 00:45:30,770
<font color="yellow">Chief Secretary Moon.</font>

593
00:45:30,770 --> 00:45:31,800
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

594
00:45:31,800 --> 00:45:35,140
<font color="yellow">I looked into the people in the Secretary's Office.</font>

595
00:45:36,170 --> 00:45:37,640
<font color="yellow">I can charge you for embezzlement.</font>

596
00:45:38,640 --> 00:45:39,640
<font color="yellow">Embezzlement?</font>

597
00:45:41,340 --> 00:45:42,340
<font color="yellow">Embezzlement?</font>

598
00:45:42,700 --> 00:45:44,070
<font color="yellow">That never happened.</font>

599
00:45:48,240 --> 00:45:51,240
<font color="yellow">That's the company's credit card statement...</font>

600
00:45:52,340 --> 00:45:54,070
<font color="yellow">and records of your operating expenses.</font>

601
00:45:56,170 --> 00:45:57,570
<font color="yellow">Explain those to me.</font>

602
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:01,000
<font color="yellow">These were fabricated.</font>

603
00:46:01,340 --> 00:46:02,670
<font color="yellow">I swear that...</font>

604
00:46:03,200 --> 00:46:04,440
<font color="yellow">these purchases were never made.</font>

605
00:46:35,300 --> 00:46:36,300
<font color="yellow">Do Gwang Woo.</font>

606
00:46:37,500 --> 00:46:39,970
<font color="yellow">I worked here my whole life.</font>

607
00:46:41,740 --> 00:46:42,870
<font color="yellow">Now, I'll spend...</font>

608
00:46:43,840 --> 00:46:46,570
<font color="yellow">the rest of my life working towards tearing you down.</font>

609
00:47:28,240 --> 00:47:29,240
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan.</font>

610
00:47:30,670 --> 00:47:32,440
<font color="yellow">When will you wake up?</font>

611
00:47:33,870 --> 00:47:35,700
<font color="yellow">I can't leave until you do.</font>

612
00:47:41,300 --> 00:47:42,300
<font color="yellow">Because of you,</font>

613
00:47:43,170 --> 00:47:44,770
<font color="yellow">my life changed in many...</font>

614
00:47:47,900 --> 00:47:50,070
<font color="yellow">Can you hear me?</font>

615
00:47:52,000 --> 00:47:53,000
<font color="yellow">Do it again.</font>

616
00:47:53,800 --> 00:47:55,000
<font color="yellow">Move your fingers.</font>

617
00:48:08,440 --> 00:48:09,700
<font color="yellow">He moved.</font>

618
00:48:10,240 --> 00:48:11,600
<font color="yellow">I saw his fingers twitch.</font>

619
00:48:18,800 --> 00:48:20,070
<font color="yellow">Were you mistaken?</font>

620
00:48:20,740 --> 00:48:21,770
<font color="yellow">I'm positive.</font>

621
00:49:12,700 --> 00:49:15,170
<font color="yellow">I haven't seen you glare like that in a while.</font>

622
00:49:17,840 --> 00:49:21,370
<font color="yellow">This is what I wanted from you.</font>

623
00:49:22,340 --> 00:49:25,600
<font color="yellow">Lonely, angry and determined to win.</font>

624
00:49:29,300 --> 00:49:30,340
<font color="yellow">But then,</font>

625
00:49:31,040 --> 00:49:32,770
<font color="yellow">I noticed your eyes...</font>

626
00:49:33,940 --> 00:49:35,140
<font color="yellow">begin to glaze over.</font>

627
00:49:36,700 --> 00:49:39,170
<font color="yellow">You forgot who you are and why you're here.</font>

628
00:49:40,900 --> 00:49:41,970
<font color="yellow">Then again,</font>

629
00:49:41,970 --> 00:49:43,470
<font color="yellow">you were blinded by love.</font>

630
00:49:44,100 --> 00:49:45,640
<font color="yellow">No wonder you lost touch.</font>

631
00:49:48,670 --> 00:49:52,040
<font color="yellow">Is that why you sided with Gwang Woo?</font>

632
00:49:52,540 --> 00:49:53,870
<font color="yellow">It's business.</font>

633
00:49:54,970 --> 00:49:57,170
<font color="yellow">Nothing more, nothing less. You said so yourself.</font>

634
00:49:58,700 --> 00:50:01,270
<font color="yellow">Without what little expectations, pity...</font>

635
00:50:01,940 --> 00:50:03,270
<font color="yellow">and interest I had for you,</font>

636
00:50:04,540 --> 00:50:05,900
<font color="yellow">Gwang Woo was more useful.</font>

637
00:50:10,100 --> 00:50:12,370
<font color="yellow">Do you hate me for choosing him?</font>

638
00:50:12,870 --> 00:50:13,900
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

639
00:50:14,900 --> 00:50:16,220
<font color="yellow">I hate you...</font>

640
00:50:16,220 --> 00:50:19,000
<font color="yellow">for bringing me into this disaster.</font>

641
00:50:26,040 --> 00:50:27,240
<font color="yellow">The deal with Gwang Woo...</font>

642
00:50:28,200 --> 00:50:29,340
<font color="yellow">is for one year.</font>

643
00:50:31,800 --> 00:50:32,800
<font color="yellow">One year from now,</font>

644
00:50:33,470 --> 00:50:34,900
<font color="yellow">I'll sign a new one.</font>

645
00:50:35,700 --> 00:50:37,970
<font color="yellow">It could be with him or with you.</font>

646
00:50:43,200 --> 00:50:44,640
<font color="yellow">Get rid of your excess baggage.</font>

647
00:50:45,440 --> 00:50:47,700
<font color="yellow">Your father, women, friends.</font>

648
00:50:48,870 --> 00:50:50,170
<font color="yellow">Start again.</font>

